title: Adam Andrew - A Path Laid Out For You [2014]
description:
Adam Andrew is a contemporary folk guitarist and singer. He began writing songs at a young age, drawing inspiration from the likes of Nick Drake, The Smiths, The Cure, Bob Dylan and Radiohead.

Adam has been performing his unique style of powerful vocals and lyrics over americana folk and bluegrass-inspired acoustic guitar since November 2012.
